  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个关于医院财务激励博弈的流程图，核心是Cost-shifting game，它连接着Placement game和Pressure。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Shift",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Cost-shifting game是起点。Placement game和Pressure是并列的下游节点吗？还是说Pressure本身也有其他指向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Shift",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，两者并列。而且Placement game本身也会指向Pressure，形成一个递进关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把这三个节点连好了。接下来Pressure指向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Pressure会同时指向Clinical risk和Signalling game，这是公共信号的两个效应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press",
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。Signalling game后面还有延伸吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Signalling game指向Bargaining game，而且Clinical risk也会反向指向Signalling game，形成一个回路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "回路已画好。Bargaining game还有什么关联？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Bargaining game和Bailout game是双向的，互相指向。另外Definition game也会指向Bargaining game。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "双向箭头我记下了。Definition game的上游是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Coding game指向Definition game，同时Compliance game也指向Definition game，这两个是并行输入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "结构清楚了。还有遗漏的节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有一个Integration game，它要同时指向Cost-shifting game和Clinical risk，作为整体框架的锚点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Integr",
        "Shift",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Integration game已加入。现在所有节点都齐了，我需要处理一下Compliance game和Pressure的关系——它们之间应该有个特殊的连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Compliance game和Pressure是双向虚线连接，表示审计压力与公共信号之间的反馈，但不是直接的因果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "虚线双向连接已设置。现在来区分一下节点类型吧，哪些属于同一类别？",
      "elements_involved": [],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Bargaining game、Signalling game、Definition game、Cost-shifting game、Placement game、Coding game、Compliance game、Bailout game、Integration game这九个是一类，用蓝色系。Clinical risk和Pressure是另一类，用红色系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Signal",
        "Define",
        "Shift",
        "Place",
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Integr",
        "Risk",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Integration game也在蓝色组？它同时连接两个红色节点，视觉上会不会混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Integr",
        "Risk",
        "Shift"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Integration game本质上是整合机制，属于蓝色组。它指向红色节点只是说明作用范围。另外Pressure需要单独高亮，用更深的红色填充和粗边框。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式都应用了。蓝色组用#DFF1FF填充、#0B5FA5边框；红色组用#FFE0E0填充、#B23B3B边框；Pressure单独用#FFD1D1填充、#8F1F1F边框，3px粗细。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Signal",
        "Define",
        "Shift",
        "Place",
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Integr",
        "Risk",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "边框粗细有区分吗？红色组的两个节点应该比蓝色组更粗一些，体现风险警示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
